Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:07.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:19.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:22.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:29.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:37.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:43.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:59.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:13.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:17.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:30.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:07.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:19.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:22.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:29.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:37.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:43.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:59.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:13.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:17.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:30.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:20.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:29.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:38.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:47.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:58.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:07.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:16.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:27.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:20.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:29.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:38.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:47.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:58.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:07.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:16.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:27.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…選哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你是要給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友們一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我就猜是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子之間互相交換巧克力也很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿茲特克文明  咖啡因  可可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊  夏奈你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  情人節跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反正會用天生的貪婪的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那些受歡迎的男生手裡搶巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊！可以吃個夠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這可不是在給你提什麼好建議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  夏奈也一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送禮不如收禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  這可是女孩子的慶典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏奈也要一起做  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶典…節日  節日！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要反擊了！睡衣派對上春香的招待實在太搶眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會又想什麼歪點子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  把大家都叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召開情人節慶典！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:27.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第7碗  越嚼越甜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要穿成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿珍  是女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節是女孩子的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不參加怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？你想說自己不是女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們的友情還真是短暫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…以後不准出入這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我做就是了  我會努力幫忙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐  我能幫什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼樣的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…啊  可愛點的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把巧克力分成小塊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我會把它切得更碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼我要來這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是節日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算送給誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會送啦  那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給哥哥？怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  真是個孤僻的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很孤僻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等你很久了  快點兒進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很孤僻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你要送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田要把巧克力送給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完全沒想過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒計劃的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  你要把巧克力送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給爸爸  昨天做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  一群無聊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說夏奈你要送誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只負責收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  要你們兩個來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  反正有空嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真礙事  給我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣小氣小氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈還是一樣那麼有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍要把巧克力送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過機會難得  送給男孩子怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想送的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想送的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  原來有那樣的對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  你見過阿真？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄他吧  他就是個智障兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  這不是備用的巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果真是個孤僻的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？哲學性的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我動手  可還是會緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  怎麼就化不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微火…超微火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  融化的巧克力也夠美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！做什麼呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試吃一下就光光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不錯  就那樣繼續拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼擅長家事  你隨時都可以嫁人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了  我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  冬馬  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力貌似不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買回來  馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不趕緊去買  你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈不也吃巧克力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤岡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  買完東西回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…夏奈叫我去買巧克力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？南讓你買  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個  因為讓我幫她做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要男生幫忙嗎  那我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…你看…可能是準備送給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不願意被本人看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南給我…巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你  讓我遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等稍微凝固一下  就可以裝飾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經凝固了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說還早呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像買完東西就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒耐性的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了阿珍的巧克力  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是沒給阿真  沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概明白他是白癡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  給我巧克力吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剩下那些你隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  抱歉  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  千秋要送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞  別害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那兒胡說八道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不管送誰  對方能高興就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  好吃吧  這可是為你特製的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚都流出來啦  開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(蠢貨)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  幫幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  現在別煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  我來幫你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…春香姐姐  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣盯著我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  千秋  你慢慢做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有男生可以送就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是個小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就開始搞這些你情我愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃不做的傢伙沒資格這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受對方  巧克力就毫無價值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有人會因為這無價值的東西而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節真是無可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一份人情巧克力也不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全都還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是誰送的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  你是不是收了很多巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個也沒有收到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個機會把巧克力送給藤岡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能收下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防止別人送巧克力給藤岡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點讓開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要站那兒多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有要送的跡象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倉鼠  你看～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倉鼠也想要巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我的巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便喂它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  收下巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為冬馬比男生還要帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  也給我們一些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  接著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回你可是名副其實的男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  讓我吃塊巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然春香做什麼都好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  保坂學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什麼時候把這個送給她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了最高級的比利時巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾盡全力所做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是南春香白色情人節的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春香並沒有給保坂學長巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有計劃隨便行動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這學校誰最受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那傢伙應該還剩很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道藤岡去哪兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他猛地衝出去  四處還巧克力去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是討厭吃巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把下一節課要用的資料拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是一個班的還要麻煩你  真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  順便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦  這個巧克力拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好  真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你不給他巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不明擺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到的全都還回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可最後也沒收到南同學的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  一臉兩手空空的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有很多哦  分一點兒給不受歡迎的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  我給你們兩個的情人節禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～謝謝你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  千秋你到底送給誰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(春香姐姐  謝謝你)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  希望有一天你不是給我而是給真正喜歡的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對春香姐姐是一心一意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉簡直太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊  你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃膩這又黑又甜的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我舔鹽去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道笊籬蕎麥和蒸籠蕎麥的區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是過去用的蘸汁不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笊籬蕎麥用的首鍋湯汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸籠蕎麥則用再煎熬的湯汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只知道加紫菜的是笊籬蕎麥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～突然想吃蕎麥麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:45.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第8碗  「游泳池是同父異母的姐妹」
